%2F194751%2F4%401200x1200.jpg&h=085828da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「山下花野子」的其中一條貼文在短短一天內就有7萬多人閱讀，但隔天再打開她的微博，發現有關她弟弟打疫苗去世的帖文已經全部被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2021-04-17/3156185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2021-04-17%2F3156185&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL3ocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=c1441ab8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2021-04-17/3156185</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"一定係收咗美國錢做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b5f7247309538a277e696c43c85f1a6bfda74c","tid":2492769,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:16:44.000Z","msg":"講明滅活疫苗"},{"pid":"51a4ac5b813e93afd358cecf96095d270b22a1f5","tid":2492769,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"叫多啲香港公安打咪幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}